---
interface Props {
  title?: string;
  subtitle?: string;
}

const {
  title = 'Why Now, Why Dark Matter?',
  subtitle = 'A three-lens narrative: market timing, technological shift, and fund edge.',
} = Astro.props as Props;
---

<section class="hero-shell relative min-h-[80vh] lg:min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-16 sm:px-10 lg:px-16">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-linear-to-b from-background/70 via-background to-background/95" />

  <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10">
    <header class="space-y-4 max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-accent/80">
        Dark Matter Bio
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-balance text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight text-foreground">
        {title}
      </h1>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-base sm:text-lg text-foreground/80">
        {subtitle}
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.4fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start">
      <!-- Left: stacked story with timeline accent -->
      <article class="hero-panel relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 sm:p-7 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="absolute inset-y-4 left-3 w-px bg-linear-to-b from-accent/40 via-accent/20 to-transparent" />
        <ol class="space-y-6 pl-6 text-sm sm:text-base text-foreground/85">
          <li class="relative">
            <div class="absolute left-[-1.35rem] top-0 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent shadow-[0_0_0_4px_rgba(156,133,223,0.35)]" />
            <h2 class="text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted-foreground">
              Compression of Breakthroughs
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              The half‑life between fundamental bioscience discovery and market application is collapsing,
              pulling forward entire categories of longevity and healthspan investment.
            </p>
          </li>

          <li class="relative">
            <div class="absolute left-[-1.35rem] top-0 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary shadow-[0_0_0_4px_rgba(102,67,226,0.40)]" />
            <h2 class="text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted-foreground">
              Data as a Biological Sense Organ
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Continuous biomarker streams, multi‑omics, and real‑world evidence turn health into a
              live data problem instead of episodic lab work, opening venture‑scale software and
              infrastructure layers.
            </p>
          </li>

          <li class="relative">
            <div class="absolute left-[-1.35rem] top-0 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-secondary shadow-[0_0_0_4px_rgba(205,196,237,0.38)]" />
            <h2 class="text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted-foreground">
              Distribution Wants Better Health Outcomes
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Employers, payers, and consumers are aligned on outcomes, not procedures. That shift in
              demand surface rewards ventures that can prove compounding, measurable improvements.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </article>

      <!-- Right: structured "why us" scorecard view -->
      <aside class="hero-panel rounded-2xl border p-6 sm:p-7 backdrop-blur-sm flex flex-col gap-5">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-accent/80">
          Where Dark Matter Inserts Itself
        </h2>

        <dl class="space-y-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-foreground/85">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] gap-x-3 gap-y-1 items-baseline">
            <dt class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted-foreground">
              Network
            </dt>
            <dd>
              Trusted access at the intersection of translational researchers, builders, and distribution
              partners who can actually route breakthroughs into the market.
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] gap-x-3 gap-y-1 items-baseline">
            <dt class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted-foreground">
              Pattern Library
            </dt>
            <dd>
              A curated set of venture and bio patterns—what tends to work, where companies stall,
              and which signals matter early—that compresses founder learning cycles.
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] gap-x-3 gap-y-1 items-baseline">
            <dt class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted-foreground">
              Time Horizon
            </dt>
            <dd>
              A willingness to underwrite compounding advantage over a decade instead of chasing
              short‑term narrative trades.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
